ACADEMIC CITATION REQUIREMENT:

This implementation is based on the research paper:
"An efficient collaborative filtering approach based on Bhattacharyya coefficient and user-item correlation"
Published in Applied Intelligence, Springer (2020)
DOI: https://doi.org/10.1007/s10489-020-01775-4

If you use this software in academic research, please cite both:
1. This implementation repository
2. The original research paper mentioned above

RESEARCH ETHICS:
This software is provided for research and educational purposes. Users are 
expected to follow ethical guidelines for recommendation systems and respect 
user privacy when implementing in production environments.
